songs.comment_text:
Hard to believe these memories are from 25 years ago.... a quarter of a century.
tunes like this one trigger an emotional response in me, something that is deeper than nostalgia, it hurts but i love it, i want to cry and turn it off, but i come back , hoping that it will be easier but... it never is...
A strange sort of LOVE.
PEACE

songs.post_title: Progressive '90 remembering Imperiale, Insomnia, Jaiss... ( DISCO STORIA )
songs.comment_text: I spent most of my high school days skipping school, skipping home and running all over the country to parties in abandoned warehouses. There was a time I felt guilty for neglecting my studies, but seeing all the people in the comments here, regrets are none. I thought I was one of few who felt so strongly about the old techno and trance - stupid me didn't realise I was always hanging out with my family :)
